Being from NYC and having a "regular" barber, I was apprehensive about getting a cut in Vegas.
As soon as I walked in I was greeted by George, who told me I was next up.
Not bad for not having an appt.. After I explained what I wanted done, I just sat back and let him do his thing.
I was very pleased with the outcome, but was expecting a heavy bill due to the fact that George did my fade, goatee, hot lather towel and shave, and even shaped up my eyebrows.
